From Chris Lilley Subject Re CorelDraw Bitmap to SCODAL In article r rsiINN , writes Does anyone know of software that will allow you to convert CorelDraw CDR files containing bitmaps to SCODAL, as this is the only format our bureau's filmrecorder recognises Corel Draw will do it version onwards If you have version perhaps an upgrade is in order Another alternative would be to use a different bureau that can take PostScript Chris Lilley Technical Author, ITTI Computer Graphics and Visualisation Training Project Computer Graphics Unit, Manchester Computing Centre, Oxford Road, Manchester, UK M PL Internet C C L Voice Fax Janet C C L